{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":16690,"name":"","username":"Marcin","avatar_template":"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/m/958977/{size}.png","created_at":"2017-03-17T13:07:12.052Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eHi,\u003cbr\u003e\nHow triangles are counted in DebugHud? I see that I have counted about 8 times more than it is in models. What could be the reason for this surplus?\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":1,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-03-17T13:07:12.052Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":11,"reads":56,"readers_count":55,"score":81.2,"yours":false,"topic_id":2916,"topic_slug":"triangles-calculation-in-debughud","display_username":"","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[{"id":2,"count":1}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":577,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":16691,"name":"Eugene Kozlov","username":"Eugene","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/eugene/{size}/902_2.png","created_at":"2017-03-17T13:28:35.462Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eMore info, plz. Shadows, viewports, text, anything.\u003cbr\u003e\nE.g. screenshot of Uhro window.\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":2,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-03-17T13:28:35.462Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":null,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":55,"readers_count":54,"score":21.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":2916,"topic_slug":"triangles-calculation-in-debughud","display_username":"Eugene Kozlov","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"read":true,"user_title":"Core developer","title_is_group":false,"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":484,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":16702,"name":"Konstantin Tomashevich","username":"KonstantTom","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/konstanttom/{size}/203_2.png","created_at":"2017-03-17T16:13:04.670Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eI found same problem some time ago. DebugHud always add its text triangles to summary triangles count. It adds about 10000 triangles if DebugHud is in DEBUGHUD_SHOW_ALL mode.\u003c/p\u003e","post_number":3,"post_type":1,"updated_at":"2017-03-17T16:13:04.670Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":2,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":52,"readers_count":51,"score":10.4,"yours":false,"topic_id":2916,"topic_slug":"triangles-calculation-in-debughud","display_username":"Konstantin Tomashevich","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_wiki":false,"link_counts":[{"url":"http://discourse.urho3d.io/t/11768-triangles-for-only-10-cubic-meshes/3058/4","internal":true,"reflection":true,"title":"11768 triangles for only 10 cubic meshes","clicks":3}],"read":true,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"username":"Eugene","name":"Eugene Kozlov","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/discourse.urho3d.io/eugene/{size}/902_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"actions_summary":[],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":333,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":true,"wiki":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false},{"id":37883,"name":"","username":"UrhoIsTheBest","avatar_template":"https://avatars.discourse-cdn.com/v4/letter/u/7feea3/{size}.png","created_at":"2020-06-12T05:58:59.702Z","cooked":"\u003cp\u003eSorry to reply this old post.\u003cbr\u003e\nI am having the same question.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eI have two terrains, each is constructed by a 65*65 heightmap.\u003cbr\u003e\nSo for each terrain, I expect 64 * 64 * 2 = 8192 triangles. Total would be \u003cstrong\u003e~16,000 triangles.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nBut I am seeing \u003cstrong\u003e61,559 triangles instead,\u003c/strong\u003e about \u003cstrong\u003e4 times more\u003c/strong\u003e!\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eAttached two screenshots.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eOverview\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/original/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/oWipRPX44cWHbVsPTRGQX8YJ1gx.png?dl=1\" title=\"image\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d_2_663x500.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"oWipRPX44cWHbVsPTRGQX8YJ1gx\" width=\"663\" height=\"500\" srcset=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d_2_663x500.png, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d_2_994x750.png 1.5x, https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d_2_1326x1000.png 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/standard17/uploads/urho3d/optimized/2X/a/aecb3136da4f111df03a7e762e46be77ce85441d_2_10x10.png\"\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"meta\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"t